#

Tossed Garden Salad with Mixed Greens and Veggies

10 min
$8
180 kcal
Difficulty: 5%
Servings: 2

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-FreeLow-Calorie

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Salad

Tags:

SaladHealthyVegetarianQuick

Description

A refreshing and crunchy salad filled with vibrant veggies and a tangy dressing, perfect for a light meal or side dish.

Ingredients

  • mixed greens (e.g., spinach, arugula, romaine): 4 cups
  • cherry tomatoes: 1 cup
  • cucumber: 1 medium
  • carrot: 1 large
  • red bell pepper: 1 medium
  • avocado: 1 medium
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • balsamic vinegar: 1 tablespoon
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • dried oregano: 1 teaspoon
